'''Sahra Axmed Maxamuud''' oo ku magac dheer '''Sahra Halgan''', waa fannaanad Soomaaliyeed oo u dhaqdhaqaaqda dhaqanka.<ref>[http://www.somalilandsun.com/somaliland-sahra-halgan-preserving-culture-and-singing-for-recognition/ "Somaliland: Sahra Halgan, Preserving Culture and Singing for Recognition"]. ''Somaliland Sun''.</ref>

== Shaqo ==
Halgan dabadeed baxay si Yurub magan galo una soo kabsado, waxaydegay [[Lyon]].<ref>"[https://www.thebeijinger.com/blog/2017/09/21/former-refugees-musical-remedies-qa-socially-conscious-somaliland-singer-sahra A Former Refugee's Musical Remedies: Q&A With Somaliland Singer Sahra Halgan Ahead of Sep 27 DDC Gig"]. ''The Beijinger''.</ref> Waxaa la siiyay qaxootinimo siyaasadeed. Waxay ka shaqeysay shaqooyin aan fiicneyn gudaha magaalada, ka qeyb qaadashada nolosha xaafadda oo ku soo laabatay muusig.<ref>https://edition.cnn.com/2017/07/12/world/somaliland-famous-singer-hargeisa-africa/index.html.</ref> Sannadkii 2009-kii ayay soo saartay albumkeedii ugu horreeyay ''[[Somaliland (album)|Somaliland]]'', kaas oo aan jawaab badan ka helin.<ref>http://somalilandstandard.com/sahra-halgan-political-refugee-status-at-transmusicales.</ref> Ka dib waxay ka shaqeysay mashruuc labaad, seddexaad oo ay la socdaan fanaaniinta Aymeric Krol iyo guitarist Maël Salètes, kuwaas oo ku kulmay Lyon. Albumkeedii labaad, ''[[Faransiskiyo Somaliland]]'', waxa uu soo baxay 2015. Muusiggu waxa uu isku daray Tuareg rock iyo laxanka Bariga Afrika.<ref>https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-49394351.</ref>

Sannadkii 2015-kii, waxay dib ugu soo laabatay inay ku noolaato Somaliland, ka dib markii ay u kala gooshaysay gobolkii ay u dhalatay iyo Faransiiska.  Waxay xarun dhaqameed u heellan fanka iyo suugaanta ka aasaastay Hargeysa oo ah magaaladii ay ku dhalatay iyo caasimadda Somaliland. Waxay soo saartay album saddexaad, ''[[Waa Dardaaran]]'', ee 2019.<ref>https://pan-african-music.com/en/sahra-halgan-waa-dardaaran</ref><ref>http://www.rootsworld.com/reviews/halgan-20.shtml</ref>

